author: rich
msg: Fixed a test break I caused with revision 326358, which moved commons-collections.jar out of our webapp template.  I thought it was only needed by XDoclet, but it turns out that StrutsTestCase (which we use in our JUnit tests) also requires it, and it was picking up the jar implicitly from the webapp classpath.
